data.value:
v1.10.0 • Added global hotkey to bring window to foreground (Ctrl-E)
v1.9.9 • Bug fixes and enhancements to the save to text file feature.
v1.9.8 • Added ability to save current template to a text file.
v1.9.6 • Added Description text box at bottom so users can add descriptive text that will not be copied.
v1.9.2 • AutoBackup feature added • AutoBackup settings added to Settings page • User can set frequency in days and location of backup
v1.9.1 • Clear button after a search returns application to opening state • Added Settings menu under Tools • Added Settings form to save Default Template to use when opening app
v1.8.9 • Fixed issues saving template from search • Saving changes now applies the Type correctly no matter where you are • Fixed sorting issue on Export display
v1.8.7 • Added Apply to font dialog • Auto-refresh moved to new Tools menu • Updated button animations
v1.8.3 • Updated action icons • Download link updated
v1.8.1 • Created new install / update model • Will check for new updates every 7 days • Added check for update button to About screen • Cleaned up some code and comments • Added code to check for previous versions file when upgrading to 1.7.x or higher
v1.6.5 • Import has been rewritten. Overwrite and Insert options are now available. • Search text is now highlighted in the text box. • Font dialogs added to both the listbox and main textbox.
v1.6.2 • New Export feature allows you to save any or all of your templates to an XML. • The OLD Export function is now called Backup. • Added ability to change color scheme of list and text boxes. • Link to GitHub site for downloading latest version.
v1.5.x • Search now checks name and text of template • Relabeled buttons • Type dropbox opens on click • Added splash screen • Added right click dialog to template list • Main text box is now rich text -- Gives more functionality ability in the future • Fixed issue with rich text box copy no line feeding correctly
